commit_message:
use value to replace dict[key]

for example:
              for key in dict:
                  if dict[key]:
                      ...

we can use value to replace it:
              for key, value in dict.items():
                  if value:
                  ...

Change-Id: I41caa60edfb7faff2a68e26056cb9a48f9c978f7

